text: Kachkarinsky () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Samosdelsky Selsoviet, Kamyzyaksky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 177 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 12 km south-west from Kamyzyak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kamyzyaksky District
title: Kachkarinsky
